title: The Dillinger Escape Plan x Jarren Benton – “Rage”  (OFFICIAL AUDIO STREAM)
description:
Stream and download “Rage” here: www.conversecons.com/consep

“Rage” is the third single off of the second Converse CONS compilation, CONS EP Vol. 2, with more singles coming this fall. The song was partially recorded at Converse Rubber Tracks in Brooklyn, New York. 

Produced by: Dillinger Escape Plan x Jarren Benton 
Music by: Dillinger Escape Plan
Lyrics by: Jarren Benton 
Vocals by: Jarren Benton 
Scratches by: DJ Hoppa
Mixed by: Aaron Bastinelli
Mastered by: Mike Bozzi
